    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable choice for a buyer who values functionality over a perfect appearance. Mechanically, the car is sound and drives well, though it is due for standard maintenance soon. The exterior shows its age with various scratches, some paint fading on the hood, and a few small dents. Inside, the cabin is intact but shows noticeable wear on the upholstery and carpets. It is a solid, honest car that still has plenty of life left for daily commuting.",
