    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of maintenance typically reserved for private collections. Mechanically exhaustive and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this specimen offers a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire an investment-grade vehicle of unparalleled integrity.",
