    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours-level condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system. Mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox, the drivetrain remains tight with documented rod bearing service and a reinforced rear subframe for maximum torsional rigidity. The chassis maintains its original geometry, supported by a factory-spec M-variable limited-slip differential and perfectly damped McPherson/multi-link suspension. Finished in pristine Alpine White over Cinnamon Nappa leather, this M3 boasts impeccable panel gaps, original VIN tags, and a flawless undercarriage. A turn-key investment for the discerning purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
